in my opinion it is C ;
because as you can read the last sentence indicating that we should take into consideration that users who are assigned to these roles accounts payable manager /senior accounts payable clerk, might change their roles in the future so we need to set the notifications to users rather than roles .

2nd point that I would like to highlight is that the tab recipient is linked to the notifications section and NOT to the assignment section THIS IS WHY we need to account for both user's roles accounts payable manager and senior accounts payable clerk.
